full_retweet_text: After resumption of flight ops, #AAI's @aaicbeairport got connected to @aaichnairport @DelhiAirport @BLRAirport by @IndiGo6E & @flyspicejet and adhered to all preventive measures regarding #COVID19. 369 pax arrived & 349 departed.
